    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ ながい・りゅうたろう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n逓相、拓相、外務政務次官、民政党幹事長、大政翼賛会常任総務・東亜局長"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"05n.html\">一覧　（ナ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=books-jp%26keyword=%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25BA%2595%2520%25E6%259F%25B3%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2583%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　石川県出身。同志社、関西学院を経て、早稲田大を卒業後、オックスフォード大に留学。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　帰国後、早稲田大で植民政策、社会政策、名著研究、英語を講ずる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　また、<a href=\"../p/osigenob.html\">大隈重信</a>主宰「新日本」の主筆として論陣を張る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　憲政会から衆議院選挙に立候補し当選。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　原内閣を批判、「西にレーニン、東に<a href=\"../p/htakasi.html\">原敬</a>」と演説し懲罰を受ける。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　外務次官、民政党幹事長などを歴任後、<a href=\"../1932/saito_1.html\">斉藤内閣</a>に拓相として初入閣。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　以後、<a href=\"../1937/kono1_1.html\">近衛内閣①</a>の逓相、<a href=\"../1939/abe_1.html\">阿部内閣</a>の逓相兼鉄相を務める。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　大政翼賛会では常任総務、東亜局長などに就任。大日本育英会の創立とともに会長。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
